					<li> Linear Algebra and Matrix Analysis </li>
					<li> Combinatorics and Graph Theory </li>
					<li> Applications in Neuroscience, Biology, and Economics</li>
					<li> Applied Discrete Mathematics</li>
					<li> Dynamical Systems and Control Theory</li>
